text:
Extremely delicious and succulent pork! 🐷😋

Their char siew 🍖 is so sweet and caramelized. very chewy and amazing. Their noodles are elastic and not too salty.

叉烧烧肉面 was originally $5 and now its $6.10 including takeaway. I think its still so worth with how much meat they give you!

The 3 malaysian men who own the stall are hardworking and have been cooking since 5-6 years ago :)
Small portion and very slow in service. Look at the photo can tell it's pathetic portion. This is from the Teck Whye branch. Do not patronize them.
$5.50 chicken and char siew rice with free soup of the day. Spicy chilli sauce 😋👍✨😋

Felt that it’s overpriced over the roasted meat and Char siew at $10 for a small portion. The half duck at $23 seems fair .
Will update if it’s delicious .

One of the best Roasted Pork & Char Siew in Ang Mo Kio.
Especially Char Siew, it is crispy and tender, melt in your mouth.
Price are reasonable too.
